events.name: Kansas State Wildcats at UCLA Bruins

headlines.description: Quarterback Brett Hundley led No. 14 UCLA to a 31-6 halftime lead, and the Bruins held off No. 11 Kansas State 40-35 on Friday night in the Alamo Bowl.
headlines.shortLinkText: UCLA roars to lead, slips K-State

headlines.description: Mason Rudolph threw for 299 yards and two touchdowns, Desmond Roland ran for 123 yards, and Oklahoma State held off Washington 30-22 in the TicketCity Cactus Bowl on Friday night.
